query:
UPDATE notebook_headers 
				SET hash = $1, 
					changed_accounts_root = $2, 
					changed_account_origins = $3, 
					chain_transfers = $4, 
					end_time = $5,
					tax=$6, 
					block_voting_power=$7,
					block_votes_root=$8, 
					block_votes_count=$9, 
					best_nonces=$10,
					finalized_block_number=$11,
					blocks_with_votes=$12
				WHERE notebook_number = $13
